features: 🪒Experience The Perfect Shave: Most razor rash comes from going over the same skin too many times. Our double edge razor blades are sharp enough to easily shave off hair, reducing the need to shave the same skin too many times. It's the perfect gift for your sensitive skin.

🪒Fits All Standard Safety Razors: BULIMICA double edge safety razor blades can be perfectly matched to all standard safety razors. Of course, you are more than welcome to choose BULIMICA safety razors, each of which has been tested thousands of times in use to achieve the optimal blade exposure angle. We hope that every user will have the best shaving experience!

🪒Highest Quality Platinum Coated Stainless Steel：Our double edge safety razor blades are made of USA stainless steel for a long lasting, precise and easy shave, it can save you time and money. High-precision platinum coated completely prevents rust, retains their sharpness and smoothness.

🪒10 Cartons of 5 Double Edge Safety Razor Blades: Each of the double edge razor blades is individually wrapped in wax-paper for safer handling. 5 pieces in a small inner packing enable you to keep and carry easily during traveling or business trip. Each piece can give on average 3 to 5 or more smooth shaves. This is a great value blades pack.

🪒BULIMICA Professional Services: We are so confident in our double edge safety razor blades and we are happy to serve you for life. If you have any questions or you are not completely satisfied with it, please feel free to tell us, our customer service will provide a satisfactory solution for you within 24h!

💖Warm Tips💖 1. This item only contains 50 count double edge blades, not include safety razors or blade disposal case in the picture. If you also want safety razors, please visit our store. 2. Please make sure the blade is installed correctly when you use it, otherwise the safety razor blade will not work properly. 3. Safety razors are different from cartridge razors, Please apply less pressure or no pressure when using it, use short and gentle strokes.
